data.description: Are you looking for a modern ranch home  on a basement with tons of upgrades? Then this house is for you! This 3 bed. 2 bath home has been recently renovated to give you the best in modern living.  From the updated kitchen with quartz countertops and new SMART appliances to the brand new flooring, every detail of this semi open floor plan is just right.  NEW HVAC, new tankless water heater and new garage doors  to make your living here even more enjoyable and care free. The house also features a large unfinished basement, great for extra storage or potential to make it your own. This stylish home is located in a great neighborhood with NO HOA and a huge backyard.
